<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'Pixel Wave Logistics — Freight & Parcel Network' }) %>
<%- include('partials/header', { active: 'home' }) %>

<div class="hero hero-photo" style="background-image:url('/css/photo-1609143739217-01b60dad1c67.jpeg');">
  <div class="eyebrow">FREIGHT &amp; PARCEL NETWORK</div>
  <h1>Every shipment,<br>broadcast in real time.</h1>
  <p class="lede">Pixel Wave Logistics moves freight and parcels across land, sea, and air. Every package carries a live signal, from pickup to the last mile.</p>
  <div class="signal-track"></div>

  <form class="form-row" action="/track" method="get">
    <input type="text" name="tn" placeholder="Enter tracking number, e.g. PW-4821-KTQ7" autocomplete="off">
    <button class="btn" type="submit">Track shipment</button>
  </form>
  <div class="hint">Tracking numbers are issued when a shipment is registered by Pixel Wave staff.</div>
</div>

<div class="stats-row" style="margin-bottom:60px;">
  <div class="stat" style="background:transparent;border-color:var(--line);"><b style="color:var(--amber);">120+</b><span>Countries served</span></div>
  <div class="stat" style="background:transparent;border-color:var(--line);"><b style="color:var(--amber);">24/7</b><span>Live tracking</span></div>
  <div class="stat" style="background:transparent;border-color:var(--line);"><b style="color:var(--amber);">3</b><span>Service tiers</span></div>
</div>

<div class="section-title">Three ways we move your world.</div>
<p class="section-sub">Air for speed, road for reach, ocean for scale — every mode reports back to the same live signal.</p>

<div class="service-grid">
  <div class="service-card">
    <div class="service-photo" style="background-image:url('/css/photo-1571086291540-b137111fa1c7.jpeg');"></div>
    <div class="icon-badge">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M2 12l19-9-7 9 7 9-19-9z"/><path d="M2 12h19"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h3>Air Freight</h3>
    <p>Time-critical shipments routed through our air network, tracked from tarmac to doorstep.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="service-card">
    <div class="service-photo" style="background-image:url('/css/photo-1600320254374-ce2d293c324e.jpeg');"></div>
    <div class="icon-badge">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="1" y="7" width="13" height="9"/><path d="M14 10h4l4 3v3h-8z"/><circle cx="5" cy="18" r="1.6"/><circle cx="17" cy="18" r="1.6"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h3>Ground Freight</h3>
    <p>Regional and cross-country trucking with live checkpoint pings at every hub along the route.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="service-card">
    <div class="service-photo" style="background-image:url('/css/photo-1670121180530-cfcba4438038.jpeg');"></div>
    <div class="icon-badge">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M3 15l2 5h14l2-5z"/><path d="M6 15V5h9l3 10"/><path d="M9 5V2"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h3>Ocean Freight</h3>
    <p>Full and partial container loads for bulk cargo, with customs milestones logged automatically.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="testimonial-section">
<div class="section-title">What shippers are saying.</div>
<p class="section-sub">A few words from people who've watched their freight move across the map.</p>

<div class="testimonial-grid">

<div class="testimonial-grid">
  <div class="testimonial-card">
    <div class="quote-mark">&ldquo;</div>
    <p class="quote">I used to email three different people to find out where a container was. Now I just check the tracking page. It's saved us hours every week.</p>
    <div class="author"><b>Priya N.</b>Founder, Loom &amp; Leaf Goods</div>
  </div>
  <div class="testimonial-card">
    <div class="quote-mark">&ldquo;</div>
    <p class="quote">The status updates actually mean something — location, timestamp, a real note. Our customers stopped asking us "where's my order" every day.</p>
    <div class="author"><b>Marcus T.</b>Operations Lead, Anchor Supply Co.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="testimonial-card">
    <div class="quote-mark">&ldquo;</div>
    <p class="quote">Switched our regional freight over six months ago. Fewer surprises, and when something does slip, we hear about it before our customers do.</p>
    <div class="author"><b>Dana R.</b>E-commerce Manager, Northfield Outdoors</div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
